  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version:\r\nVersion: 1.7.0-unstable\r\nGit Commit: 17ce0a37de5a2712a8bf9d58df705e718b3b2cd6\r\nArchitecture: amd64\r\nProtocol Versions: [63 62]\r\nNetwork Id: 1\r\nGo Version: go1.8.1\r\nOperating System: linux\r\n\r\nOS & Version: Ubuntu 16.04.2 LTS (64 bit)\r\n\r\nCommit hash : master branch (17ce0a37de5a2712a8bf9d58df705e718b3b2cd6)\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\n\r\nClean shutdown\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\n\r\nPanic on shutdown\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\n\r\nwas running geth with full node sync, synced to head, then stopped it and ran it with following flags:\r\n``` bash\r\n./build/bin/geth --nousb --cache 2048 --vmodule les=5,light=5 --lightserv 50\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe light client server was generating new CHT, this was the last one generated before shutdown:\r\n```\r\nTRACE[08-09|15:45:55] Generated CHT                            number=217     root=0x06bdaa0f9d1ebe88f6601f762c09ba2ade88f68b581ec77dcf2b3e666e071a5c\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### Backtrace\r\n\r\n````\r\n^CINFO [08-09|15:45:56] Got interrupt, shutting down... \r\nINFO [08-09|15:45:56] IPC endpoint closed: /home/gs/.ethereum/geth.ipc \r\nINFO [08-09|15:45:56] Blockchain manager stopped \r\nINFO [08-09|15:45:56] Stopping Ethereum protocol \r\nINFO [08-09|15:45:56] Ethereum protocol stopped \r\nINFO [08-09|15:45:56] Stopping light Ethereum protocol \r\nINFO [08-09|15:45:56] Terminated topic registration            topic=LES@d4e56740f876aef8\r\nINFO [08-09|15:45:56] Light Ethereum protocol stopped \r\nINFO [08-09|15:45:56] Transaction pool stopped \r\npanic: Canonical hash not found\r\n\r\ngoroutine 4590 [running]:\r\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/les.makeCht(0x16db380, 0xc4200720d0, 0xc4c7755920)\r\n\t/home/gs/go/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/build/_workspace/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/les/server.go:383 +0x505\r\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/les.(*ProtocolManager).blockLoop.func1.1(0xc423b5c010, 0xc42023e8c0, 0xc423ab43c0)\r\n\t/home/gs/go/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/build/_workspace/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/les/server.go:315 +0x4a\r\ncreated by github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/les.(*ProtocolManager).blockLoop.func1\r\n\t/home/gs/go/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/build/_workspace/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/les/server.go:321 +0x829\r\n````\r\n",
