    "body": "Looks like `hash := core.GetCanonicalHash(db, num)` returns the empty hash because the DB is shutdown?\r\n\r\nThis code is running in a routine spawned at https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/master/les/server.go#L277\r\n\r\nI'm guessing this routine should listen to a shutdown message emitted in https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/master/les/server.go#L89 to conform to the service behavior defined at https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/master/node/service.go#L74\r\n \r\n",
